The paper discusses security and privacy issues in cloud computing, which are major concerns in the field of computer security (cs.CR). It also describes various service and deployment models of cloud computing, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The challenges related to service quality and interoperability are also discussed, which are relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY). Finally, the paper proposes solutions to mitigate these challenges, which involves data science and machine learning techniques (cs.DS).
